### List reminders
GET http://localhost:3000/api/reminders

### Create reminder
POST http://localhost:3000/api/reminders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "recipeId": "{{recipeId}}",
  "scheduledAt": "2026-04-25T15:00:00+02:00",
  "title": "Time to bake bread",
  "message": "Don't forget to start the sourdough!"
}

### Delete reminder
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/reminders/{{reminderId}}

### Internal: Send single reminder
POST http://localhost:3000/api/internal/reminders/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "recipientEmail": "test@example.com",
  "recipeId": "abc123",
  "recipeName": "Sourdough Bread",
  "title": "Recipe Reminder",
  "message": "Time to bake your sourdough bread!",
  "appUrl": "http://localhost:4200"
}

### Internal: Send batch reminders
POST http://localhost:3000/api/internal/reminders/batch
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "greeting",
  "userIds": ["user1@example.com", "user2@example.com"]
}
